Sane install instructions
---------------
Prereq. lodo db and a functional customer db.

Ubuntu:
apt-get install libapache2-mod-php5 php5-mysql

Linux:
Point virtualhost to /html folder
Create lodo database and create customer datbase
Set up conf/prefs_customer.inc, conf/default.inc and conf/prefs_lodo.inc

Make the following symlinks:
ln -s html lodo
cd lodo
ln -s index.php lib.php

Update the Password field of person of the customer database with the mysql password function.
